ster Card－－八達通的同類技術。有港民形容：「當年英國在香港試行八達通，可謂當時科技先驅。今日倫敦已棄用慢人一步的二維碼技術，到非入閘處拍卡、提升速度，香港卻去發展落伍了的二維碼。這就是香港主權移交前後的分別。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n早前班五毛重死撐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n話二維碼先進個班五毛呢？係時候出黎護航<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2352c63c5900a616886e794522fba047eebcfe9b","tid":905093,"uid":35430,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c68ab1c95906d38d8095359f763fd44b35bc01f9","tid":905093,"uid":176991,"like":166,"dislike":1,"score":165,"quote":{"pid":"ab366d171bbfa0b78b44e53a19d7313a8c505218","tid":905093,"uid":130901,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"除左中國，仲有咩先進國家鍾意吹自己用晒流動支付？"},"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:46:37.000Z","msg":"外國已經用緊nfc ，部手機解鎖當八達通咁拍就得，大陸用QR code呢啲過晒時嘅野都仲好意思打飛機<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:51:28.000Z","msg":"咁你就要問下連登班五毛喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8a5c5b39a5fa3ec5267c201946fc1174aed51e40","tid":905093,"uid":41714,"like":6,"dislike":10,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:54:08.000Z","msg":"依家食個lunch, 就知有幾多人用支那寶俾錢， 多到你唔信。 老麥大家樂呢d, 隨時10個人， 有一半都會用支那寶俾"},{"pid":"e9dbec0fc3c9cf8ea8fc69daacb5be209210232e","tid":905093,"uid":176991,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"4f3c57ec62e53b80512820b798f349282d41135a","tid":905093,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"quote":{"pid":"c68ab1c95906d38d8095359f763fd44b35bc01f9","tid":905093,"uid":176991,"like":166,"dislike":1,"score":165,"quote":{"pid":"ab366d171bbfa0b78b44e53a19d7313a8c505218","tid":905093,"uid":130901,"like":84,"dislike":1,"score":83,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T01:34:52.000Z","msg":"除左中國，仲有咩先進國家鍾意吹自己用晒流動支付？"},"citedBy":5,"r